**Attack Reaction** - Destroy this: **Mark** target opposing hero.

**Battleworn**

**Action** - Destroy this: Until end of turn, whenever you play an attack action card with stealth, gain {r}. **Go again**

**Battleworn**

**Attack Reaction** - {r}, {t}: Target attack with stealth gets "When this hits a hero, **mark** them."

**Blade Break**

**Attack Reaction** - Destroy this: Target attack with stealth gets **go again**

**Arcane Barrier 1**

**Stealth**

When this attacks, the next attack with stealth you play this combat chain gets **go again**.

**Stealth**

When this hits a hero, choose 1 at random;
- They choose a card in their hand. Banish it.
- They choose a card in their arsenal. Banish it.
- Banish the top card of their deck.

**Stealth**

When this attacks, it gets the base abilities of the last attack action card with stealth you control on the combat chain.
Your attacks with stealth get +1{p} this turn.
